title: The Soft Moon “Wrong” - Converse Red Light Session
description:
The Soft Moon’s ‘Wrong’ is dark and throbbing; one long, static bassline punctuated by punchy, electronic drum beats that are supported by the wooden racket of Luis Vasquez’s sticks and macabre, modified vocals.

www.thesoftmoon.com
www.facebook.com/theso
